est day.</li>
	<li>Globally, almost all banks are closed on Sundays.</li>
	<li>Months that begin on a Sunday will have a Friday the 13th in them.</li=
>
	<li>Super Bowl Sunday, which is the championship match between the top two=
 teams from the National Football League (NFL), is one of the largest sport=
ing events. </li>
